title: Boats catch fire at Quincy Marina - Massachusetts news
text:
Firefighters are battling fires aboard multiple boats at Quincy Marina.
Quincy Police shared this video of the fire on its Twitter account .
 Fire crews on scene of boat fire at Cove Way pic.twitter.com/cqbCojekSH
— Quincy Police (@quincymapolice) October 8, 2015 The fire broke out after 7:30 a.m. Thursday morning.
A picture taken earlier by Lt. Gillan of @quincymapolice Marine Unit of boat fire at Cove Way pic.twitter.com/jw53mgpUJK
— Quincy Police (@quincymapolice) October 8, 2015 Boats on fire at Quincy Marina @fox25news pic.twitter.com/266SmVFUto
— Julie Grauert (@JulieGrauert) October 8, 2015 We’ll have more information as it becomes available.
